Keeping so many older patients from being readmitted to hospitals seemed like a good idea. Now some experts aren't so sure. https://t.co/04DH4ZFnct
Decreases In Readmissions Credited To Medicareâ€™s Program To Reduce Hospital Readmissions Have Been Overstated | Health Affairs https://t.co/O3ACtz1bgg
Decreases In Readmissions Credited To Medicareâ€™s Program To Reduce Hospital Readmissions Have Been Overstated | Health Affairs https://t.co/f2G32OPdwH

More on the #HRRP

Decreases In Readmissions Credited To Medicareâ€™s Program To Reduce Hospital Readmissions Have Been Overstated | Health Affairs https://t.co/uDEdK5CULR
